  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/f1acd9256ddd6b901a2509b2b0ac319a.poster.avif?t=1694662168\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/f1acd9256ddd6b901a2509b2b0ac319a.webm?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/f1acd9256ddd6b901a2509b2b0ac319a.mp4?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>EMBARK EPIC ADVENTURE</u></strong><br>Over 4+ stunning stylized worlds, each with its own unique style, procedural dungeon, handcrafted locales, fearsome foes and empowering bosses. Fight through the dungeon to empower yourself first and then defeat the final boss with your skills and strategy. Return to the center island, choose next world to go and vanquish them all. Finally challenge the Void Lord after you slayed all other bosses!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/24a8cd8d765ce63b750aee9ae8e5f165.poster.avif?t=1694662168\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/24a8cd8d765ce63b750aee9ae8e5f165.webm?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/24a8cd8d765ce63b750aee9ae8e5f165.mp4?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>CRAFT NEW COLOR SHARDS</u></strong><br>Obtain color cores from fallen bosses, and use them to craft new color shards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/ef65790c1714f2dc0eac8d06070c2cc0.poster.avif?t=1694662168\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/ef65790c1714f2dc0eac8d06070c2cc0.webm?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/ef65790c1714f2dc0eac8d06070c2cc0.mp4?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>SEEK OUT LEGENDARY RELICS OF POWER</u></strong><br>Over 50+ relics add endless possibilities to each loop. Collect legendary relics, combine them with your own strategy or synthesize to a new one. Experiment with color shards and explore your own lore.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/bfbb19fd7633efea795eb5cdd9a42b9b.poster.avif?t=1694662168\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/bfbb19fd7633efea795eb5cdd9a42b9b.webm?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/bfbb19fd7633efea795eb5cdd9a42b9b.mp4?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>TAME & LEVEL UP YOUR BATTLE COMPANIONS</u></strong><br>Tame new battle companions, adventure with them to gain experience and level their attributes up.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/f65bb3f933272bf5dc8d7a8a2d480237.poster.avif?t=1694662168\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/f65bb3f933272bf5dc8d7a8a2d480237.webm?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/f65bb3f933272bf5dc8d7a8a2d480237.mp4?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>INFINITY POSSIBILITIES</u></strong><br>With procedural generated dungeon, dynamic map, random loots and props, each loop offers unforgettable gaming experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/e8d7f65306bbadb32a6a8e8a359466ac.poster.avif?t=1694662168\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/e8d7f65306bbadb32a6a8e8a359466ac.webm?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/e8d7f65306bbadb32a6a8e8a359466ac.mp4?t=1694662168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>JOIN OUR DISCORD SERVER FOR MORE!</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109020/extras/8882c0355cd5c4d75c39c9093ec45073.avif?t=1694662168\" width=652 height=320 /></span>",
